the school play starts...

40:10.107 --> 40:11.165
Empty auditorium.

40:12.343 --> 40:15.176
Hey...

40:15.212 --> 40:16.873
What are you girls doing?

40:16.914 --> 40:18.575
Nothing.
Nothing.

40:18.616 --> 40:21.244
