going to do with you,

40:58.989 --> 41:01.014
but we're going
to talk.

41:01.058 --> 41:03.219
Some of Janie's experiments
really creep me out.

41:03.260 --> 41:07.526
I wonder if she'll grow up
to be a billion-IQ genius,

41:07.564 --> 41:09.828
or a total nutcase.

42:12.730 --> 42:14.721
Sport, Sport...

42:23.307 --> 42:24.899
Chicken man.

42:31.382 --> 42:33.043
Do it again, do it again.

42:47.798 --> 42:50.289
Sport.

42:50.334 --> 42:52.825
Sport...

42:52.870 --> 42:54.861
Sport!

42:56.173 --> 42:58.038
Help me.

43:01.779 --> 43:03.906
Hey, Harriet.

43:03.947 --> 43:05.414
Hey.

43:05.449 --> 43:08.043
All right, come on.

43:19.263 --> 43:21.288
How does it look?

43:21.331 --> 43:23.822
