44:27.764 --> 44:28.924
Yeah, yeah, come on.

44:28.966 --> 44:30.058
Strike a pose.

44:39.042 --> 44:42.739
Spy route: Brand-new stalk.

44:42.779 --> 44:45.270
Home of Agatha K. Plummer,

44:45.315 --> 44:49.479
