54:07.444 --> 54:09.207
Mystery!

54:09.246 --> 54:10.907
Hold on, you guys,
you guys.

54:10.947 --> 54:11.936
Listen, listen, listen.

54:12.048 --> 54:13.413
"The only thing more pathetic

54:13.450 --> 54:14.815
