54:43.713 --> 54:44.941
Janie...

54:44.981 --> 54:46.676
Janie, Janie, Janie...

54:46.716 --> 54:47.876
Come and get it.

54:47.918 --> 54:49.442
Read it. Come on.

54:49.486 --> 54:50.976
What does it say?

54:51.087 --> 54:53.317
- Come on.
- Janie, Janie.

54:53.356 --> 54:55.381
"Janie really
creeps me out."

54:55.425 --> 54:56.585
Ooh.

54:56.626 --> 54:59.720
"I wonder if she'll grow up
to be...

54:59.763 --> 55:02.129
