someone would kick Beth Ellen."

55:17.481 --> 55:18.607
Oh!

55:21.852 --> 55:23.820
Uh, Laura.

55:23.854 --> 55:29.087
"Laura Peters...
her face looks totally...

55:29.125 --> 55:30.251
pinched."

55:30.293 --> 55:32.625
Oh.

55:37.501 --> 55:39.492
"If I were the boy
with the purple socks...

55:40.504 --> 55:42.631
I'd hang myself."

55:44.341 --> 55:46.468
Something else.

55:46.510 --> 55:47.738
Cut it out, Marion.

55:47.777 --> 55:50.177
Oh.

55:50.213 --> 55:52.443
Maybe there is something
in here for Sport.

