Ooh, harsh.

56:23.346 --> 56:25.211
Oh, oh, oh.

56:26.316 --> 56:28.511
That's mean.

56:28.552 --> 56:31.180
Sport, I...

56:31.221 --> 56:32.347
I-I got to go.

