56:34.190 --> 56:35.953
I got to make spaghetti.

56:35.992 --> 56:37.983
I can't stay here anymore.

56:40.196 --> 56:42.460
Harriet...

56:42.499 --> 56:45.434
sit over there till we decide
what to do with you next.

56:46.703 --> 56:47.863
Wait. What's this?

56:47.904 --> 56:49.769
"I learn everything I can

56:49.806 --> 56:52.331
"and I write down everything
