57:48.798 --> 57:50.857
Ole Golly, Ole Golly,

57:50.900 --> 57:54.802
Ole Golly, Ole Golly,
Ole Golly.

57:54.838 --> 57:57.272
Harriet?

57:57.307 --> 57:58.638
I said

57:58.675 --> 57:59.801
I'm fine.

57:59.843 --> 58:01.936
Really.

