Lookit.

58:23.165 --> 58:24.359
Oh, my God.

58:31.541 --> 58:33.566
Hey, Sport.

58:37.580 --> 58:39.571
Janie.

58:41.551 --> 58:42.984
You hear something?

58:43.986 --> 58:45.977
No.

59:02.538 --> 59:03.903
Plug this in over there.

59:03.940 --> 59:05.066
Over there?

59:05.107 --> 59:07.075
Um, well, that one's closer.

59:07.109 --> 59:09.805
Carrie? Carrie?

59:13.549 --> 59:14.777
Oh, my...

