01:31:29.917 --> 01:31:33.148
That... is that.

01:31:33.187 --> 01:31:35.519
Yes.

01:31:58.746 --> 01:32:00.714
I am on a mission
to be a great writer.

01:32:02.850 --> 01:32:04.283
A good friend once told me

01:32:04.318 --> 01:32:07.810
that all great writers
try to see everything.

