is a difficult,

01:33:48.322 --> 01:33:50.222
but not impossible, process.

01:33:50.258 --> 01:33:52.658
Mostly, you've got to want
to be cured.

01:33:56.130 --> 01:34:00.533
But I'm pretty sure
it's a two steps forward,

01:34:00.568 --> 01:34:03.594
